thread.title: Domino's Pizza Enterprises Says ‍FY18 Guidance On New Store Openings Is Between 310-330 Stores For Group

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Domino's Pizza Enterprises Says ‍FY18 Guidance On New Store Openings Is Between 310-330 Stores For Group

organizations.name: pizza enterprises says ‍fy18 guidance on new store

text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Domino’s Pizza Enterprises Ltd:
* HAS UPDATED SSS GUIDANCE FOR AUSTRALIA AND NEW ZEALAND, NOW EXPECTED TO BE +6-8% FOR FULL YEAR VERSUS +7-9%
* ‍FY18 GUIDANCE ON NEW STORE OPENINGS IS BETWEEN 310-330 FOR GROUP, INCLUDING HALLO PIZZA CONVERSIONS​
* ‍GROUP STORE COUNT TARGET REMAINS AT 4,650 STORES BY 2025​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
